title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The behavior of calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before or after data extraction is unclear.
EB: The method IMetaData.getColumnLabel() should return the same labels before and after data extraction.
SR:
1. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before data extraction. 
2. Extract data using some method. 
3. Call IMetaData.getColumnLabel() after data extraction. 
4. Compare the labels returned in step 1 and step 3. They should be the same.
